# Qwen2.5-VL / Qwen2-VL vision tower (Qwen/Qwen2.5-VL-3B-Instruct)
#
# The text backbone is a standard Qwen2 decoder living at model.layers.* —
# it is carried by _LAYER_PATTERNS + _GLOBALS untouched. This table carries
# the VISION TOWER (visual.*) which the old encoder dropped entirely.
#
# Verified against Qwen/Qwen2.5-VL-3B-Instruct safetensors header (2026-05-24):
#   visual.patch_embed.proj.weight   [1280, 3, 2, 14, 14]  Conv3d (temporal=2, 14x14)
#   visual.blocks.N.norm1.weight     [1280]                RMSNorm (no bias)
#   visual.blocks.N.norm2.weight     [1280]                RMSNorm (no bias)
#   visual.blocks.N.attn.qkv.weight  [3840, 1280]          fused QKV (3*1280)
#   visual.blocks.N.attn.qkv.bias    [3840]
#   visual.blocks.N.attn.proj.weight [1280, 1280]
#   visual.blocks.N.attn.proj.bias   [1280]
#   visual.blocks.N.mlp.gate_proj.*  [3420, 1280]          SwiGLU gate (SiLU)
#   visual.blocks.N.mlp.up_proj.*    [3420, 1280]          SwiGLU up
